              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A titanium layer saturated with deuterium atoms on a",
                "molybdenum backing was used as a target. The target",
                "diameter was 11 mm. The mean thickness of the target",
                "was 1.40+-0.06 mg/cm2 at the deuterium atom",
                "concentration of 56+-2%. The thickness of the carbon",
                "build-up on the target surface during the experiment",
                "was 28 mu-g/cm2."
              ]
            }
          ],
